  {
    "type": "EXPOSITORY (ENGLISH BIBLE)",
    "name": "The Treasury of David",
    "elements": [
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "5 Commit thy way unto the Lord, trust also in him; and he shall bring it to pass.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "6 And he shall bring forth thy righteousness as the light, and thy judgment as the noonday.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "Psalm 37:5",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "verse-link",
            "text": "Psalm 37:5",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "\"Commit thy way unto the Lord.\" Roll the whole burden of life upon the Lord. Leave with Jehovah not thy present fretfulness merely, but all thy cares; in fact, submit the whole tenor of thy way to him. Cast away anxiety, resign thy will, submit thy judgment, leave all with the God of all. What a medicine is this for expelling envy! What a high attainment does this fourth precept indicate! How blessed must he be who lives every day in obedience to it! \"Trust also in him; and he shall bring it to pass.\" Our destiny shall be joyfully accomplished if we confidently entrust all to our Lord. We may serenely sing - ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "\"Thy way, not mine, O Lord,",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "However dark it be;",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "O lead me by thine own right hand,",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "Choose out the path for me.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "Smooth let it be or rough,",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "It will be still the best;",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "Winding or straight, it matters not,",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "It leads me to thy rest.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "I dare not choose my lot,",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "I would not if Icontinued...",
        "children": []
      }
    ]
  },
